{"tid":887866,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【藍潔瑛逝世】林建明曾予援手 慨嘆：佢唔係普通情緒病，折磨得佢好重","createTime":"2018-11-03T09:14:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T10:23:43.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8b953e9eb3ac71f43d0254867265a80422114384","tid":887866,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T09:14:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jNDkgd4qV7jexdvl6fpwLA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9MzYw/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/b9ebc10352c6e1d3027238e00842cc36\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FjNDkgd4qV7jexdvl6fpwLA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9MzYw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fb9ebc10352c6e1d3027238e00842cc36&h=38e80cac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙姐林建明是「心晴行動」創辦人，亦曾向藍潔瑛申出援手，今日沙姐接受蘋果電話訪問，語調平靜說：「近排太多人離開，生老病死係必然。自己就咁睇，人世上有任務，可能完成咗就離開去第二度。我覺自己都有兩個任務，完成後都隨時行得，但要保密。有啲嘢冇計，時間夠鐘。」<br />\n沙姐歎藍潔瑛非普通情緒病，她說：「佢係有病，唔係普通情緒病，折磨得佢好重，不論家人、朋友都有幫過佢，但真正幫到佢嘅人係自己，無論父母子女都只能扶你一把。佢係病得幾重，乖乖食藥係可以保持到，唔食藥就病發，好多人都申出過援手，但真正靠自己，可能世上任務完咗，希望佢安息。」<br />\n沙姐表示二人雖然未合作過，但以前都有不少共同朋友，有一段時間還同屬陳自強公司旗下，而最後一次見面都是數年前的事。"},{"pid":"ee844dfcbb8db952a5898dcdae39a0d37808c7a2","tid":887866,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T09:16:32.000Z","msg":"YouTube<br />\n曾志偉回應強姦藍潔瑛事件 抽絲剝繭解構可能性〈蕭若元：八卦蕭析〉2018-01-18<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mgJDoZjXQQ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmgJDoZjXQQ4&d=lEbLpYQusR8VjQlStmRoroM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=73c46d3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mgJDoZjXQQ4</a>"},{"pid":"924ef60be90e5b4f62db3d18777a8dec8e56e7c2","tid":887866,"uid":207087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T10:21:16.000Z","msg":"回頭是岸，邊到會有耶穌"},{"pid":"b2e2ceb1d582e173d8d73aff4bd8b97f71410539","tid":887866,"uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":0